# Configuration Files

The project uses several configuration files to define its behavior:

## WXT Configuration
- [wxt.config.ts](mdc:wxt.config.ts) - Configures the WXT build system, extension permissions, and modules

## TypeScript Configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript compiler options and project settings

## UI Configuration
- [components.json](mdc:components.json) - Configuration for UI components system
- [postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs) - PostCSS configuration for processing CSS
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind CSS configuration

## Linting and Formatting
- [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs) - ESLint configuration for code linting

## Browser Extension Configuration
- [web-ext.config.ts](mdc:web-ext.config.ts) - Configuration for web-ext, a tool for building/testing extensions
